    "body": "I don't know if it's relevant to our discussion but I have two use cases that we often see:\n- when first displaying the page, display a content page instant of the empty query (a query with no parameters set)\n- when there are no results, display a list of all the refinements so that the end-user can discard some of them to get back to a state with results\n",
