    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "After second thought, even with the above api, basic limitation appear (like you're not able to access the query when hitting no results). \n\nIn the end, for the release, we're just gonna create a \"Conditional Display\" guide explaining how to use the `createConnector` function to build it. \n",
